{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d31f6143-f12b-406a-a7eb-3d7314c2cb30", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d31f6143-f12b-406a-a7eb-3d7314c2cb30@1.pkg/1772602376775/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602377446", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d31f6143-f12b-406a-a7eb-3d7314c2cb30@1.pkg/1772602376775/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602377446"}, "identifier": "d31f6143-f12b-406a-a7eb-3d7314c2cb30", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>最后两句诗在《步出夏门行》各章末尾都有，是诗歌合乐时所加的套语，与正文内容没有直接关系。所以题目中的表述不恰当。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对《观沧海》这首诗的赏析不正确的一项是（　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列对《观沧海》这首诗的赏析不正确的一项是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d31f6143-f12b-406a-a7eb-3d7314c2cb30@1.pkg/item.json?v=1726318287475", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这首诗通过写作者在远征途中登上碣石山俯瞰大海所看见的壮观景象，展现了诗人宽广的胸襟。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>诗歌前八句写诗人登上碣石山看见山岛耸立，树木茂盛，大海波澜壮阔的景象。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;日月之行，若出其中；星汉灿烂，若出其里。&rdquo;通过丰富的想象，写出沧海之大，吞吐日月，含盈群星的气派。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>最后两句诗，如一曲雄壮的乐曲，在最激越处戛然而止，悲从中来，发出感慨。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对《观沧海》这首诗的赏析不正确的一项是（　　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "d31f6143-f12b-406a-a7eb-3d7314c2cb30", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对《观沧海》这首诗的赏析不正确的一项是（　　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"t